          "reviewBody": "All reviews are false positive, please don't get trap. Only School is having good infrastructure. Everything else is rubbish. Government public school is far better than this.\nSchool has no quality in education. Teachers are also not hardworking and honest. Whether it is principal or class teacher or teacher, no body takes thier own responsibility. They leave everything on parents. Only they are focusing on extra curricular activities which are on  paid basis, in which also they seek parents support  for efforts and hard work.\nThier moto is to just earn money, nothing to take with education.\nTeachers are very lenient in marking and teaching. Thier knowledge and will is doubtful. Only the talent they have is how to defend themselvs from blame. Most of the time they are not checking copy , and when they are checking ,they tick mark correct for wrong spellings and answers.",
